{"tid":1309634,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[正撚量] 其實送中條例只針對犯左法嘅人","createTime":"2019-07-12T09:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T05:49:02.000Z","uid":168703,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"531bc48f1a7766aa98f98cb49c927749524e51c4","tid":1309634,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:42:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>中國監獄 (2004年)</strong><br />\nA: 兄弟 干了什麽事进来了<br />\nB: 就是抢东西啦 坐三年 你呢<br />\nA: 开车撞死人啦 坐五年<br />\n<br />\n<strong>都係中國監獄 (2020年)</strong><br />\nA: 你衰咩入黎坐呀<br />\nB: 我著左黑色衫出街... 你呢<br />\nA: 我係迪士尼買左隻小熊維尼...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYoFtad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYoFtad.png&h=81b41a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>見身邊嘅人呢排都因為成個香港嘅環境感到好壓抑，想大家心情舒緩返啲，同時又唔想大家松懈落黎，無咩叻淨系識鳩up，想試下用一個輕鬆啲嘅方式去講下政治野。你有一秒覺得好笑我都覺得自己成功左架啦，好笑嘅比個正評或者遞比身邊個人睇下，將呢份笑容傳開去。</em></span>"},{"pid":"5386d51c67eaa43ff34c913e6b2fe7e937f7e863","tid":1309634,"uid":168703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"除此之外，同朋友傾過想開埋個ig分享下呢啲訊息，始終有啲人真係懶到連懶人包都唔會睇，希望呢啲輕鬆啲好笑啲嘅post可以帶佢地了解下政治情況，如果可以嘅大家follow埋呢個ig同share比多啲人呀！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/positivelunface?igshid=10f52mz5bkc08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpositivelunface%3Figshid%3D10f52mz5bkc08&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=4d9909da\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/positivelunface?igshid=10f52mz5bkc08</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>另外都仲有其他post架可以睇埋呀！</em><br />\n<br />\n[正撚量] 到底有冇暴動呀屌？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309462</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[正撚量] 今日想同大家簡單咁討論下評分系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1307610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1307610</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13f3f9af963780b4fddd4e4eeb81fddfb7adc387","tid":1309634,"